			"			float hemiDotNormalHalfGround = 0.5 * dot( normal, hemiHalfVectorGround ) + 0.5;",
			"			float hemiSpecularWeightGround = specularTex.r * max( pow( hemiDotNormalHalfGround, shininess ), 0.0 );",

